content.rendered:
Directed by Buchi Babu Sana

Written by Buchi Babu Sana. Buchi Babu Sana. Buchi Babu Sana. Krushna Hari. Jayanth Panuganti

Cast Panja Vaisshnav Tej(Aasi). Krithi Shetty(Sangeeta). Vijay Sethupathi(Rayanam). Gayatri Jayaraman(Raayanam’s wife). Sai Chand(Jalayya). Mahadevan(Raayanam’s father (as Rama Raju)).Brahmaji. Rajeev Kanakala(MRO). Naga Mahesh(Govindu). Jaya Krishna(Thalimpu).Killi Kranthi.Ravi Varma. Rajsekhar Aningi(Bus Driver). Raaghavan Murugan(Young Aasi (as Master Raghavan)).Guruswamy. Subba Rao Vepada(RMP Doctor).Ramesh Reddy.Dr. Rayala Harischandra.Vijay Kumar Yellapragada.Pavan Teja.Nalini Bandi.Dhaassyam Geetha Bhascker.Tarun Dasari.Chandramogli Madem.Tapi Mishra.Raju Naidu.Praneeta Patnaik.Mamilla Shailaja Priya.Naveena Reddy.Sony Reddy.Karan Viijay

Language Telugu

Producers Ashok Bandreddi. Chiranjeevi Pedamallu. Y. Ravi Shankar. K.V.V. Bala Subramanyam. Anil Yerneni. Naveen Yerneni.

Production Mythri Movie Makers. Sukumar Writings
